      "text": [
        "4684 - وَ قَالَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ: \"لاَ تُجْبَرُ اَلْحُرَّةُ عَلَى إِرْضَاعِ اَلْوَلَدِ وَ تُجْبَرُ أُمُّ اَلْوَلَدِ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4684 - Imam Abu Abdullah (as) said: \"A free woman cannot be forced to breastfeed a child, but a but a bondwoman (umm al-walad) can be compelled to do so.\""
        ]
      }
    }
